{"tid":415210,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"女性語文能力比男性強？","createTime":"2017-09-26T20:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T18:01:34.000Z","uid":70883,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ef470c6fc66dc815e777ab181cacf1b6b01cc608","tid":415210,"uid":70883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:09:23.000Z","msg":"是咪因為自人類識講野開始都由母親負責教小朋友講野、同佢地溝通。我認為男性原本任何一方面都比女性強，男性數論邏輯能力較強乃天性，女性語文能力較強乃習性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81b37f0864af7bd9b75a5e606d5cccb15d5878","tid":415210,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:13:21.000Z","msg":"有咩統計？"},{"pid":"01ee888c70de008f0b89ed28d7f40cfd3cd53367","tid":415210,"uid":117821,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:18:49.000Z","msg":"你講乜撚野呀？自已有語障，就怪9男人，你都on撚9"},{"pid":"27a14f8f43081fe2325fdb4854428fbb2a7cee53","tid":415210,"uid":149534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:19:47.000Z","msg":"論證過程呢？"},{"pid":"e765210ddbc51841e8a7d3bc8d2b21171ac3953a","tid":415210,"uid":44073,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5a969d8b8fa9fce22cf907c8331ec7bb3b4e5601","tid":415210,"uid":117821,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/042516_0a1dd7ec59a588246ce1e6d37449a455.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F042516_0a1dd7ec59a588246ce1e6d37449a455.gif&h=659c4a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAverage IQ female count &gt; Average IQ male count.<br />\nIndividual Difference of female &lt; that of male</blockquote><br />\n就係一張圖 就話女人語言能力比男人強 你係得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20657a6e1e8b99c755739994fef5651268d431d0","tid":415210,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T20:31:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2eac6ec27ad40553348e0b2f7b2fb0499eabdf86","tid":415210,"uid":70883,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"其實大家係咪有所誤會<br />\n我所講既語言能力其實係指表達能力<br />\n而我想討論既重點係 咩原因令女性語文能力較強<br />\n<br />\n至於點解我會有咁既前設--女性語文能力比男性強，係因為我觀察及聽聞所得，觀察就係話中小學課堂、考試表現、男女教師既分別，聞就係一向都聽到老師&amp;不少報章評論都係咁講，而從未聽過話男性表達能力比女性強之說<br />\n<br />\n我以為呢個係公認既事實所以冇拎所謂證據出黎。有人可能話最top既語言學家是男性居多，我個人認為係因為個層次去到講求用邏輯剖析語言<br />\n<br />\n至於女性語文能力較強是習性既證據我冇，我自己亦搵唔到，正因如此先拎上黎討論，睇下有冇人會有證據/認為係其他原因導致"},{"pid":"0487c1b6e973cd41eb15a4ecef67263dafd9602f","tid":415210,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T03:58:58.000Z","msg":"一般英文都係女仔叻D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e271a6e44098626dbba64b911ac417d7362c3c17","tid":415210,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:06:03.000Z","msg":"因為女人無邏輯，唯有專攻唔需要太有邏輯性既語文"},{"pid":"2bd599df05e0c32382b9c490f37f27261088b392","tid":415210,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為女人無邏輯，唯有專攻唔需要太有邏輯性既語文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0263ff03f697a609e71207d19868e081f341d8","tid":415210,"uid":32906,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/042516_0a1dd7ec59a588246ce1e6d37449a455.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F042516_0a1dd7ec59a588246ce1e6d37449a455.gif&h=659c4a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAverage IQ female count &gt; Average IQ male count.<br />\nIndividual Difference of female &lt; that of male</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔同意，我覺得大部分女人都蠢過男人"},{"pid":"21dc65c9a1a939aeb78c80f34a5e387738925a55","tid":415210,"uid":144648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"一定係啦, 中學時期都睇得出<br />\n<br />\n考評局成績report統計都好清楚<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 依加男仔比女仔好既成績只有數同物理, 而個差距愈來愈少. 因為愈出愈淺, 係玩鬥小心"},{"pid":"5ceec169794ed239f1068342cfad7505b3104ca8","tid":415210,"uid":65530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1098763f87dc537a808d39200c5083ac20051825","tid":415210,"uid":124899,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"表達能力強唔強都無乜用。<br />\n因為無邏輯。<br />\n只係用一篇好長既篇幅去講廢話。"},{"pid":"04f3405130a239f1a99c83e21fc5103966ceb829","tid":415210,"uid":21629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/042516_0a1dd7ec59a588246ce1e6d37449a455.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F042516_0a1dd7ec59a588246ce1e6d37449a455.gif&h=659c4a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAverage IQ female count &gt; Average IQ male count.<br />\nIndividual Difference of female &lt; that of male</blockquote><br />\n其實我唔同意，我覺得大部分女人都蠢過男人</blockquote><br />\n你自以為是啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447f89bd7b6c5b9d3bc9e9c15dbc71cf10df190b","tid":415210,"uid":99179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"有個說法係<br />\n<br />\n喺石器時代，男人係負責出外打獵，所以男人既體格能力發達d，而且當時出外係好危險，需要理性思考同埋群體協作，盡可能以最安全最有效率既方法打獵，所以簡短精確既語句係最好，唔需要太多感性同詞彙豐富既句子。<br />\n<br />\n反之，女人負責留喺部落處理好多日常事務，同埋最重要係交換情報資訊，盡量掌握提高生存率既資訊（e.g.疫症、天災、製衣、生活技能等），所以語言天份係會好d，要經常進行社交。<br />\n<br />\n所以除左講出語言天賦既分別外，亦引申左其他分別，想知再講。"},{"pid":"54f2e1b7ce8613f3f0862d6cbf2670c2904d19ef","tid":415210,"uid":9732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"<bl